    {
      "id": "sybil_1_listing_1",
      "firm_id": "sybil_1",
      "description": "Hey there! I\u2019m parting with my absolute pride and joy, and let me tell you, she is a total stunner! This beauty is in truly pristine, mint condition\u2014it honestly feels like it just rolled off the showroom floor. I\u2019ve babied this car from day one, keeping it garaged and spotless, so it\u2019s ready for a new home where it\u2019ll be just as loved. It drives like a dream and looks even better in person. Come take a look and see for yourself!",
