    {
      "id": "sybil_9_listing_2",
      "firm_id": "sybil_9",
      "description": "This E46 M3 is a superlative example of high-revving naturally aspirated engineering. Powered by the iconic S54B32 inline-six featuring individual throttle bodies and Double VANOS, the powertrain delivers linear thrust up to an 8,000 RPM redline. This collector-grade specimen features a reinforced rear subframe, documented rod bearing service, and a precise Getrag 6-speed manual gearbox. The chassis maintains factory-spec rigidity with an M-Variable differential lock providing optimal torque distribution. Finished in pristine condition with zero deferred maintenance, it offers a pure, analog driving experience that is increasingly rare.",
      "price": 46500.0,
