      "description": "Hey there! You've seriously gotta see this beauty\u2014it\u2019s honestly like it just rolled off the showroom floor. I\u2019ve absolutely babied this car, keeping it tucked away in the garage and making sure every inch stays in pristine shape. It drives like an absolute dream and still has that fresh car smell! I'm honestly a bit sad to let it go, but I'm looking for someone who will love it just as much as I have. Feel free to reach out if you have any questions or want to come take a look!",
